name: enterlude
description:
"enterlude" is the 7th song off my new beattape "souls" releaseing August 27, 2021. enterlude was something that i created that felt almost like a ship at see that had just taken off from shore and was feeling the thrill of adventure, but was on its way down from the high and going more into the calming, contemplative state of "is this really happening" type of mentality. 

the cover art was generated by AI using the text prompt "souls entering." it looks like the ai thought they were entering a judgement between the sun and the moons. 

Bop your head and enjoy the music. If you purchase this piece, hit me up on twitter @ryanartwalker and I will send you the album with high quality AIFF files!
